  Crowdfund
%section
  .container
    .row
      .col-lg-12.text-center
        %h2.section-heading Crowdfund

    .row
      .col-md-6
        %p.lead The Plan
        %p
        Entropy is an
        %strong Ethereum-powered floating experiment
        to crowd-own and steer a fleet of sailing hackspaces around the world - anyone can be part of our global community.
        %p
          We aim to make it easy to see the value of a DAO and an example of the possibilities open to all as we bravely sail into the new world.

.container
  .page-header
    %p.lead Project Entropy will be rolled out in 4 Waves:
