          %p
            %small.text-muted
              %i.glyphicon.glyphicon-time
              Minimal Viable Entropy
        .timeline-body
          %p  This wave sees us bootstrap the community, start testing ideas and confirm the projects foundations are good. Limits are in place to keep the number of Citizens, invested Ether and risk to safer levels.
